# This repository publishes ONLY the runnable prototype (which now contains its
# own ontology under prototype/ontology-ssc/). The surrounding paper (LaTeX
# sources, figures, SysML model, PDFs, drafts, literature-review artifacts,
# AI/agent output) is kept private.
#
# Strategy: ignore everything at the repo root, then re-include just prototype/.
# Files inside it are further filtered by prototype/.gitignore (venv, caches,
# .DS_Store, the external uthp-yocto clone).

# Ignore every top-level entry by default...
/*

# ...then re-include exactly what we share.
!/.gitignore
!/prototype/

# Safety net (in case any of these appear inside the re-included dirs)
**/.DS_Store
**/__pycache__/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.py[cod]
